ygData.messageBody:
Hi there

Thanks a lot for the nice welcome. :)

I reached lvl 14 today....I´m on Tallon Zek.

I´ve already printed the maps from eqatlas.com, so I only get lost
when I forget to look at my map.
Luckily I have a good old friend who tracks me down when I wander off
to some isolated part of a forest or so.
AND I´ve joined a guild today, though none of them are around my lvl.

Well, gotta go play some more....see ya

- Tiny
